{"tid":1924193,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（語重心長）唔想收皮就畀心機幫手做野啦","createTime":"2020-03-13T14:12:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-13T15:57:03.000Z","uid":163529,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a0b120de3814ae421314f49d63aab4102fd69e69","tid":1924193,"uid":163529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T14:12:32.000Z","msg":"成日以為自己Share一兩個帖就做咗野<br />\n呢班人究竟有無見到對家攻勢幾咁厲害？<br />\n成日就話唔洗理佢地，要明既人自然明，<br />\n但你地知唔知呢班五毛言論就黎成為主旋律！<br />\n舉個例👇🏻👇🏻<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qpdA7o7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqpdA7o7.png&h=5fd88e79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n你可以話Like既係五毛，<br />\n但類似既言論幾乎起好多地方都出現，<br />\n仲要係起唔少外國出名Youtuber comment出現！<br />\n當然，我知道都有唔少人做緊野，<br />\n但文宣組都多番講明而家活躍人數得幾百位，<br />\n如果大家真係唔想輸，就麻煩幫下手！<br />\n最少都當「每日任務」咁樣做，<br />\n多一份聲音，多一個Like，<br />\n已經足夠影響國際話語權！<br />\n<br />\n同埋唔好成日怪人用態度差既語氣出標題，<br />\n要知道好多人係受硬唔受軟，<br />\n咁溫和既語氣，換黎既只會係漠視！<br />\nFree-rider 你做project可以做，<br />\n但而家危急關頭唔該醒定D著緊D!"},{"pid":"b009dcd5a4ef02de1b8473b955ffe32d1e569c58","tid":1924193,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T14:13:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d669391e2171d293798b68118772f59b0df3927f","tid":1924193,"uid":163529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T14:23:12.000Z","msg":"屌又無人理"},{"pid":"32cacca3196a28ee69912c8537c82c684019fe66","tid":1924193,"uid":40666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T14:23:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19dfa4d753e693f5681c41311974ecf492bac4d2","tid":1924193,"uid":74663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T14:25:04.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"8bc5ca5b076ffe1d300e29965476ace40a990e8a","tid":1924193